lead_paragraph: Radim Vrbata has a move he likes to use in shootouts, and it worked again for a goal that helped the Arizona Coyotes beat the Nashville Predators 3-2 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Duclair, Domingue Lead Coyotes Over Predators in Shootout
